    <item>
      <title>石油需求超出预期，测试原油峰值的计算</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/oil-demand-outpaces-expectations-testing-calculus-on-peak-crude</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球石油使用量比以往任何时候都多，今年的需求再次超出预期，引发了人们对全球消费何时达到峰值的疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/oil-demand-outpaces-expectations-testing-calculus-on-peak-crude</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大宗交易中小盘股溃败削弱印度股市成交量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/smallcap-rout-dents-indian-equity-volumes-amid-big-block-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度的股票交易量已降至去年 12 月以来的最低水平，因为小公司股票的抛售减缓了散户投资者涌入印度 4.3 万亿美元市场的速度，尽管机构仍在抢购大笔交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-22/smallcap-rout-dents-indian-equity-volumes-amid-big-block-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 03:59:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利为何对中国股票保持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-22/why-morgan-stanley-remains-cautious-on-chinese-stocks-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利首席中国股票策略师劳拉·王表示，她在全球新兴市场框架内对中国市场仍然相对谨慎。她在“彭博社：中国秀”节目中与大卫·英格尔斯和伊冯娜·曼进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-22/why-morgan-stanley-remains-cautious-on-chinese-stocks-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Mar 2024 03:59:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国平安表示盈利令人失望后将恢复利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/ping-an-profit-falls-unexpectedly-on-china-stock-market-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[平安保险（集团）股份有限公司预计盈利能力将恢复，全年净利润下降 23%，导致其股价创下 2022 年 11 月以来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-21/ping-an-profit-falls-unexpectedly-on-china-stock-market-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 10:29:16 GMT</pubDate>
